54:18.046 --> 54:20.339
‐Beaten?
‐Beaten. No?

54:20.340 --> 54:21.717
Oh, yes, I've been beaten.

54:26.764 --> 54:28.389
(translating)

54:28.390 --> 54:31.267
Oh sure. Yeah. No.

54:31.268 --> 54:33.728
I know. But it's worth it.
It's worth it

54:33.729 --> 54:36.106
if it brings some more peace
and consciousness to the world.

54:37.399 --> 54:38.358
Thank you so much.

54:38.359 --> 54:40.693
Thank you so much.
Thank you. Come back.

54:40.694 --> 54:42.863
I will.

54:49.077 --> 54:50.204
Lovely time.

54:51.663 --> 54:52.247
‐All the best.
‐Thank you.

54:52.248 --> 54:55.292
Thank you. Bye‐bye.

54:56.418 --> 54:59.170
Stone:
Our American "partner."

54:59.171 --> 55:01.965
It's their favorite word.
He's used it a thousand times.

55:04.134 --> 55:06.052
‐Thank you, Dmitry.
‐All the best.

55:06.053 --> 55:08.221
‐See you later.
‐Yeah. Next time
it'll be relaxing.

55:08.222 --> 55:09.263
See you.

55:09.264 --> 55:10.598
Thank you so much.

55:10.599 --> 55:12.517
Stone: Good luck
with the military tonight.

55:12.518 --> 55:13.718
Take some time off after that.

